Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们活着追求幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神就是将点滴的幸福分给这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那人的笑容又拯救了女神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是接受了女神们的爱的男人的故事

Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:02:02.89,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HC37281&\3c&HCDE9F0&\be1}啊 许愿吧 再一次

Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从自知自身不成熟\N再次踏上旅途已过了11个月零3天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是为了像蓓儿丹蒂大人那样让众人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我净化着自己的心灵\N追求着歌唱的心灵持续着旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有歌声的地方我都会踏足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是回来报告修行成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 还真是干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺庙也很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去打个招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是小看人家的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有好好帮到姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别突然出现在人家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你把我调和的宝贵的一见钟情药给打翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  把我的集束合成爆弹弄坏的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所欠缺的是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让你们听听爱的歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番兵机雷发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一个人在那唠唠叨叨的生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 刚才就在人家的院子里吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 小丫头 这里是我的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 穿得那么轻薄心灵也堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 听我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后抛弃烦恼到我的胸膛来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的修行还不够…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没脸见蓓儿丹蒂大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再去修行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么吵闹没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又是兀儿德和诗寇蒂在吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这姐妹吵架还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她们俩关系非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像萤一和惠一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 小萤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再没这样为你着想的妹妹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你再客气点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在想因为有我在所以无法两人独处了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢人多热闹的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萤也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小萤住到这里也快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从与萤一结下签约之日起已经过了那么久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之间还有这样的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们是根据天上界的契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂她们的行动 消灭了究极破坏程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因封印冥府之门失去的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去不可修复的5%都恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 制造了多余的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次损坏的数据是助人女神事务所的登陆文件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂这样还能留在地上界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指契约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大魔王的事故让她留在地上界也是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有天要让她回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是笠原教授的讲课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要出门了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 到大学去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是森里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“是我” 请问是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是契约者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打 打给萤一？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在契约已经消灭 我也不能让女神长时间留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大魔王给你带来了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会为你考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只给你整理心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说了这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是因为大魔王 消灭它的可是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一没有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是天神大人特意和我联系…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是决定现在就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在天上界工作的助人女神事务所并不只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想并不会人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有萤一的愿望被消灭掉 总觉得不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把大魔王怎么来着消灭掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你是说是我的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大魔王支配了还很高兴地在城里搞破坏的又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想消灭这事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一点碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但关键的声音数据破损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能修复这个的话就可能修复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要契约者的声纹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将萤一的愿望再次输入系统就能修复文件了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 你没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你紧张什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音屏幕确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望像你这样的女神一直留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能通过认证 请再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我希望像你这样的女神一直留在我身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能通过认证 可能是词汇错误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会忘了自己许的愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望像你这样的女神一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有像你这样的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃你做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去参观博物馆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说出那么多还真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有错误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破损到无法通过声音认证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 蓓儿丹蒂 你不是记录下密码的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被加上了防护 所以我是不能说出密码的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有错误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这恢复记忆锤子和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德大人特制记忆恢复药剂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选哪一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我现在在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 竟然忘了和姐姐的约定 真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是用爆雷降临好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用番兵君特别攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了在做这个之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也听听萤一是怎么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 去大学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这时候了还去大学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候就需要转换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约的消灭并不是萤一的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样和你一起上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打上工也都是因为那个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 现在才能像这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我竟然忘了那个愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是不懂关于这个内燃机的燃烧率…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自动车部部员竟然连这个都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自动车部的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道廉耻吗 廉耻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就好好地教导你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…我之后还要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们还要打工 先行告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算呆在地上界也解决不了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能介入主系统调出密码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是在尽力而为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道会乱来才回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个热一下就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为萤一说了想两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们独处的时间所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样想的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能侵入主数据库 从姐姐的记忆文件中读取密码了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能完成这个黑客君的话没什么不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么做这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是为萤一的事在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样那个没用可怜虫萤一就会说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还会被姐姐夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是在微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也必须给她回应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想看到蓓儿丹蒂的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期天 天又那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人出门逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还没有决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蓓儿丹蒂约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的时间我想好好地使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去做便当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦说了是约会就紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有那种勇气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀请我约会这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就开心地渡过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算装模作样也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连牵手都做不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了收集萤一的声音资料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然蓓儿丹蒂的微笑最漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 一共是600日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天付煤气费把上个月的打工钱用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 不介意的话就请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候作为男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的打工钱我还没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就让我来付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方吃便当真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能这样多约会几次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去展望台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里风景更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要牵个手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:17:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞舞吧精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名集结  拯救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 让你救了不少次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是 我到头来什么都为你做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一总是为在我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我忘记我是因为事务所的契约才留在萤一身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蓓儿丹蒂永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能再次在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是今后就见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果萤一需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念也一定会传达过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念是永远不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想无论何时都和你这样的女神在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 如偿所愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 声音认证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认契约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德的偷窥还是有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德更是什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回地上界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直会在萤一的身边
